OL,5,G1325 Animal Farm
OL,6,     F(1954) George Orwell's cautionary
OL,7,     Ftale reimagined in cartoon form. A
OL,8,     Ffarm's animals revolt against
OL,9,     Ftheir abusive owner only for the
OL,10,     Fpigs to become drunk with their
OL,11,     Fnewly found power.
OL,12,G1455 Gun Fury
OL,13,     F(1953) Western. Rock Hudson stars
OL,14,     Fas a California-bound settler who
OL,15,     Fmust ride 1500 miles to the
OL,16,     FMexican border to rescue his
OL,17,     Ffiancee (Donna Reed) after she's
OL,18,     Fabducted by an outlaw.
